item.title: Somethings wrong with my friends character!
item.dc:creator: @LeScape_Pk LeScape Pk
item.description:
@LeScape_Pk wrote:

Kitno:

He has added someone to his friends list or he has an item that isn’t in your item.cfg. Check your character files and see if anyone is on his friends/ignore list and delete them off of it. And check if he has any items that aren’t in your item.cfg.

could be a cache issue, some places are too big to load on login, wheres his character at?
